text:
This is example blog post to test if my Github Pages are configured correctly. Let’s plot formula of the function \[
f(x) = \exp \left( \frac{1}{2}x \right) + \sin^2(x)
\]




x = seq(-1, 1, 0.01)
y = exp(x/2) + sin(x)^2
plot(x, y, type = 'l')
